ag.com\/flipkart-vs-amazon-homegrown-giant-playing-catch-artificial-intelligence\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">e-commerce giant Amazon<\/a>&nbsp;needs data science professionals to do tasks ranging from supply chain optimization, inventory, and sales forecasting to the detection of fraud.  The tech giant suggests that data scientists at Amazon form the link between business and technical sides.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Salary<\/strong>: Rs 5 lakh to Rs 45.57 lakh | Rs 15.56 lakh (average)&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"2-flipkart\">2.Flipkart<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Indian e-commerce giant&nbsp;Flipkart will provide jobs to data scientists&nbsp;across teams. Their roles that have to handle are from building Systemic Intelligence across Flipkart products to uncovering and redefining shopping trends in the country. The data science team is responsible for designing capabilities and solutions across the supply chain, fintech, consumer experience, search and discovery, demand shaping, and fraud modeling.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"3-walmart\">3. Walmart&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Flipkart\u2019s parent company Walmart has over 29 wholesale stores spread across the country in the name of \u2018Best Price\u2019. Data science professionals at Walmart will have to discover new and innovative ways of applying data across businesses while using automation to improve processes. Data scientists at Walmart are responsible for mixing technology and retail.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Salary<\/strong>: Rs 14.5 lakh to Rs 33.5 lakh | Rs 24.6 lakh (average)&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"4-hewlett-packard-enterprise\">4. Hewlett Packard Enterprise<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The goal of Hewlett-Packard Enterprise, or HPE, is to help customers manage and assess their data. It will enable them with advanced tech solutions, services, and consumption models to work on the available data.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Salary<\/strong>: Rs 10 lakh to Rs 31 lakh | Rs 21,28,671 (average)&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"5-ibm\">5. IBM<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hpe.com\/in\/en\/solutions\/data-analytics.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Hewlett Packard Enterprise<\/a>, or HPE, is looking forward to helping customers manage and assess their data. It will allow them with advanced tech solutions, services, and consumption models to work on the available data.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Salary<\/strong>: Rs 10 lakh to Rs 31 lakh | Rs 21,28,671 (average)&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"6-deloitte\">6. Deloitte<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/analyticsindiamag.com\/jobs-roundup-latest-internships-in-data-science-analytics-in-india\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Deloitte<\/a>&nbsp;will give end-to-end business solutions for data science practitioners. It will ensure that analytics is in its DNA, and thus, Deloitte\u2019s expertise lies in providing smart insights for stronger outcomes.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Salary<\/strong>: Rs 5.52 lakh to Rs 27 lakh | Rs 12.41 lakh (average)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"7-accenture\">7. Accenture<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Accenture has a&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/analyticsindiamag.com\/deloitte-accenture-it-outsourcing-market\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">diverse team of data scientists and AI experts<\/a>&nbsp;to leverage the power of AI and bring in changes in companies and in society at large. Its team of data scientists apply ethical and responsible AI to measure the impact of businesses.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Salary<\/strong>: Rs 1.87 lakh to Rs 31 lakh | Rs 10.20 lakh (average)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"8-24-7-ai\">8.  [24]7.ai<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Customer Experience software company [24]7.ai will use AI and ML to understand and analyze customer intent. It helps companies to make personalized, predictive, and seamless customer experiences across channels.&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/analyticsindiamag.com\/247-ai-steps-up-hiring-in-india-over-5k-jobs-up-for-grabs\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Data science professionals at [24]7.ai<\/a>&nbsp;are responsible for building and defining AI models into products and offerings.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Salary<\/strong>: Rs 11.27 lakh to Rs 23 lakh | Rs 19.31 lakh (average)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"9-netflix\">9.Netflix<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The fact that Netflix tops the list of tech companies offering high salaries may not be surprising. Netflix has built a strong reputation for compensating its tech professionals generously, with the understanding that these employees are expected to deliver outstanding performance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Salary:  Rs 500000<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"10-airbnb\">10. Airbnb <\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;The other companies on this list, from Airbnb will generally have the biggest of Big Data challenges, which should have data scientists with exemplary skills. To put it another way: If a data scientist tasked with making nationwide logistics more efficient isn\u2019t making six figures per year, something is very wrong.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Salary: Rs. 33,860<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"faq-10-companies-offering-data-science-highest-package\">FAQ-  10 Companies Offering DataScience  Highest  Package <\/h2>\n\n\n<div id=\"rank-math-faq\" class=\"rank-math-block\">\n<div class=\"rank-math-list \">\n<div id=\"faq-question-1703575770278\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q1. Which company gives the highest salary to data analysts?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. Optum has   \u20b9 10,12,788 per year. <br \/>Myntra has  \u20b9 9,53,834 per year.<br \/>Tiger Analytics has  \u20b9 8,79,809 per year. <br \/>Google has  \u20b9 8,50,582 per year. <br \/>IBM has  \u20b9 7,